SHA-256 of text input up to 119 bytes (1 or 2 blocks).
Multi-block: padded_byte spans block_idx + pos; iterate_blocks
recurses block-by-block, calling compress 8 times per block to
extract all 8 updated H values, then carrying the running hash
state to the next block.
Validated against sha256sum for inputs of 0, 3, 5, 43, 55, 56,
100, and 119 bytes.
sha256_word is the entry rule.
